  body.bg-triangles
    div.preloader
      div.preloader__wrap
        div.circle-pulse
          div.circle-pulse__1
          div.circle-pulse__2
        div.preloader__progress
          span
    main.main
      div.container.gutter-top
        div.row.sticky-parent
          aside.col-12.col-md-12.col-xl-3
            div.sidebar.box.shadow.pb-0.sticky-column.boxStyle
              div.avatar
                img.profilePicture(src=profilePicture, alt="Profile picture")
              div.text-center
                h3.title.title--h3.sidebar__user-name
                  b #{firstName} #{lastName}
                div.badge.badge--dark #{profession}
                div.social
                  a.social__link(href=linkedIn, target="_blank")
                    i.fab.fa-linkedin-in
                  a.social__link(href=xing, target="_blank")
                    i.fab.fa-xing
                  a.social__link(href=github, target="_blank")
                    i.fab.fa-github
                div
                  a(href=url + "/en")
                    img.flag(src=url + "/images/flags/americanFlag.png", alt="American flag")
                  a(href=url + "/de")
                    img.flag(src=url + "/images/flags/germanFlag.png", alt="German flag")
                div.sidebar__info.box-inner
                  ul.contacts-block
                    li.contacts-block__item(data-toggle="tooltip", data-placement="top", title="Birthday")
                      span.iconSpan
                        i.far.fa-calendar-alt
                      span.infoSpan #{birthday}
                    li.contacts-block__item(data-toggle="tooltip", data-placement="top", title="Address")
                      span.iconSpan
                        i.fas.fa-map-marker-alt
                      span.infoSpan #{location}
                    li.contacts-block__item(data-toggle="tooltip", data-placement="top", title="Email")
                      span.iconSpan
                        i.fas.fa-envelope
                      span.infoSpan
                        a(href="mailto:" + email) #{email}
                    li.contacts-block__item(data-toggle="tooltip", data-placement="top", title="Telephone")
                      span.iconSpan
                        i.fas.fa-phone
                      span.infoSpan #{telephone}
                  a.btn(href=url + "/downloadCV/en")
                    i.font-icon.icon-download
                    span Download CV
          div.col-12.col-md-12.col-xl-9
            div.box.shadow.pb-0
              div.circle-menu
                div.hamburger
                  div.line
                  div.line
                  div.line
              div.inner-menu.js-menu
                ul.nav
                  li.nav__item
                    a.active(href=url + "/en") About
                  li.nav__item
                    a.active(href=url + "/resume/en") Resume
                  li.nav__item
                    a.active(href=url + "/skills/en") Skills
                  li.nav__item
                    a.active(href=url + "/portfolio/en") Portfolio
                  li.nav__item
                    a.active(href=url + "/contact/en") Contact
              div.pb-0.pb-sm-2
                h1.title.title--h1.title__separate About me
                p Hello, my name is Marko Bošnjak and I'm a software and web developer currently based in Cologne, Germany. I enjoy turning complex problems into well-designed and user-friendly applications, while tending to keep my code clean and organized.
                p From an early age, I was fascinated by technology. Simply using a computer, cellphone or even playing Play Station, was never enough. I always wanted to know how things work on a deeper level. Why things happen? So I started to get involved into informatics. During my time in college, I became more and more interested in coding. Even before my master graduation, I started working at TeDev in the technical support department, gathering knowledge and evolving. Currently I'm working at venITure GmbH as a software developer, building apps for Jira Server and Cloud.
                p Besides developing, I have some other interests aswell. I enjoy playing football and doing fitness. I'm a big fan of rock music and like to attend concerts whenever I get the chance. I also like to travel, books and movies.
                p If you didn't get bored while reading this short introduction, take a look at my CV and feel free to contact me. &#128515;
              div.box-inner.pb-0
                h2.title.title--h3 What I'm doing
                div.row
                  div.col-12.col-lg-6
                    div.case-item.box.box__second
                      i.fas.fa-terminal.case-item__icon
                      div.jobDescriptionSpan
                        h3.title.title--h5 Backend development
                        p.case-item__caption Knowledge of Scripting and Compiled languages (Node.js, PHP, Java) along with MySQL and MongoDB databases
                  div.col-12.col-lg-6
                    div.case-item.box.box__second
                      i.fas.fa-code.case-item__icon
                      div.jobDescriptionSpan
                        h3.title.title--h5 Frontend development
                        p.case-item__caption Using JavaScript, HTML and CSS to provide modern and high-quality designs
                  div.col-12.col-lg-6
                    div.case-item.box.box__second
                      i.fas.fa-book.case-item__icon
                      div.jobDescriptionSpan
                        h3.title.title--h5 Documentation
                        p.case-item__caption Writing documentation in a professional way to bring applications closer to users
